# }}}
# resists {{{
color green  You feel ((especially )?healthy|hardy).
annotate /You feel ((especially )? healthy|hardy)./ Gained poison resistance.
color green  You feel (full of hot air|warm).
annotate /You feel (full of hot air|warm)./ Gained cold resistance.
color green  You (feel a momentary chill|feel cool|be chillin').
annotate /You (feel a momentary chill|feel cool|be chillin')./ Gained fire resistance.
color green  You feel ((wide )?awake).
annotate /You feel ((wide )?awake)./ Gained sleep resistance.
color green  You feel (very firm|totally together, man).
annotate /You feel (very firm|totally together, man)./ Gained disintegration resistance.
color green  Your health currently feels amplified!
annotate /Your health currently feels amplified!/ Gained shock resistance.
color green  You feel (insulated|grounded in reality).
annotate /You feel (insulated|grounded in reality)/ Gained shock resistance.
# }}}
