annotate /You feel warmer./ Lost fire resistance.
annotate /You feel cooler./ Lost cold resistance.
annotate /You feel a little sick./ Lost poison resistance.
annotate /You feel tired./ Lost sleep resistance.
annotate /You feel conductive./ Lost shock resistance
# }}}
# losing intrinsics {{{
